{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"ddaa3149d2bc6f82505f6e66070e557c3cd2a049ea4df89a74f34c4ff227a209","slug":"vendor","location":"/handbook/scm/vendor.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"供应商关系管理","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/handbook/scm/vendor.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/handbook/scm/vendor.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"vendor.md","url":"/vendor-7abce0c8147511e8946a753d801e3533.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本板块记录供应商关系管理策略，重点关注云厂商工单博弈。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"UpBvQ5pOXs"}],"key":"tDC552iu5o"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"云厂商工单博弈","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"D1fVr0MbnP"}],"identifier":"id","label":"云厂商工单博弈","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"M0zuYzlBYU"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工单系统是云厂商与客户沟通的核心渠道。厂商掌握技术细节和内部政策，形成非对称信息。不同级别的工单响应时间和服务质量差异大，工单分配机制不透明，厂商倾向于最小化投入转移成本。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"wX13pP1IB1"}],"key":"NZfMzVWRDT"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心策略","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"h6l54Qb2pD"}],"identifier":"id","label":"核心策略","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"tjGuqDcMzS"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"拒绝电话回访，坚持工单留痕；拒绝盲目配合，强制责任倒置。将技术故障转化为厂商的服务履约危机，利用差评权与重开权，倒逼高级技术资源介入，最终实现问题解决与商业补偿双赢。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"NHG5QPX5oT"}],"key":"TZELUefvMZ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建立三轮不满意差评机制。每个工单透明化差评威胁，明确告知三次不满意会差评并影响客服绩效考核、团队评级、客户满意度指标。每轮回复都要像没有上下文的AI对话一样完整独立。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"AWbZ6rIKPv"}],"key":"Wwy8pFzsnt"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"处理步骤","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"md9mNeUTBk"}],"identifier":"id","label":"处理步骤","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"bbICPMmsbl"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第一步：立规矩。封死对方逃避留痕的退路，质疑其基础排查能力，透明化三轮差评机制。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"BEOtHboZHN"}],"key":"NBJKZEHOc6"},{"type":"blockquote","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「不接受电话沟通，请所有排查逻辑和结论在工单内留痕。你们目前要截图、问版本的问法极其业余，这是在将排查责任恶意转嫁给用户。作为服务商，请先自查后台日志与虚拟化链路监控，说明为何你们无法感知到该时间点的异常。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"ORUAGhY43m"}],"key":"KpJOzym5x0"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本工单采取三轮不满意差评机制：如果连续三次回复无法提供实质性技术进展，我们将直接关闭工单并差评，然后重新开单升级。这会直接影响你们的绩效考核和服务评级。」","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"W6wNKnQnWa"}],"key":"oykmVjUnhm"}],"key":"CEFzP0bEhD"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第二步：水平判断。根据对方回复判断技术水平。套路化回复特征：只问截图/日志但无分析逻辑、引用通用文档但无针对性建议、建议重启/重装等敷衍方案、回避技术原理解释、机械复制模板。遇到套路化回复，必须反复强调不专业并要求换人。","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"I6WxUismhP"}],"key":"CpBntRngiT"},{"type":"blockquote","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「你们刚才的回复完全属于套路化敷衍，只问日志不分析，引用通用文档不给出针对性判断，这是典型的技术能力不足表现。","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"NngtFHKlfN"}],"key":"k0xbsxVBKZ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我已明确告知三轮不满意差评机制，这是第二轮回复。如果无法从技术原理层面解释该故障的根本原因，请立即升级至高级技术工程师。我们不接受继续在基础排查流程上浪费时间。","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"qzu1USe9LT"}],"key":"qeJyb8xxc9"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"请正面回答：根据你们的后台监控，该故障时间点是否有异常事件记录？如果无法自查，说明你们的排查权限级别和标准路径。如果当前客服确实无法从技术原理解释问题，请说明何时能升级至专家介入。」","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"SRLPA5clHC"}],"key":"u88obcllNx"}],"key":"PPB2YyPOyz"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第三步：控节奏。用高手问法施压，每轮回复重申差评威胁。如果对方表现出专业分析能力，可以适度配合但仍需施压争取补偿；如果对方持续套路化敷衍，直接升级至高级技术工程师。","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"QW7gVmyRe5"}],"key":"rCJHUiE6Jg"},{"type":"blockquote","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「这已经是第三轮回复，你们仍然无法提供任何实质性技术进展，继续停留在要日志、问截图的套路化层面。","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"m0ISEHnX3C"}],"key":"ZADMNWXhQn"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"根据三轮不满意差评机制，本工单即将关闭并差评。在关闭前给你们最后一次机会：如果当前客服确实无法解决问题，请立即在工单内明确说明需要升级至高级技术工程师，并提供预计升级时间。","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"HkI2KJqCUj"}],"key":"kErf20nqVC"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"否则我们将：","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"yqlxd54N0C"}],"key":"RG9b7D1IoN"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":1,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"关闭本工单并提交差评","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"r0kQrKBX9O"}],"key":"DlFXUXHn1g"}],"key":"zWWR7NUSoM"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"重新开单并要求直接分配至高级技术工程师","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"key":"NvktA4fxBW"}],"key":"HUElZgtx0S"}],"key":"QMOuDlQTVv"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"同时向客户经理投诉当前客服的服务质量」","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"key":"yYEmKOeLZL"}],"key":"cyVp1zy1HW"}],"key":"L3TfTXztu1"}],"key":"ivyp68Fqnc"}],"key":"hD5pIHR3Bh"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第四步：亮底牌。明确告知差评后果，迫使对方按规矩办事。","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"key":"ddhnac9O5y"}],"key":"O9mXgGY1vt"},{"type":"blockquote","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「请注意，本工单的所有回复都将作为后续服务质量投诉的证据。我们已执行三轮不满意差评机制，当前状态为第三轮不满意。","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"key":"DJ0QWsUySj"}],"key":"K2xRk43a7y"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果你们仍无法提供实质性解决方案，我们将立即关闭工单并差评。差评将影响客服个人绩效考核、团队服务质量评级、该云服务产品的客户满意度指标。","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"key":"xs9WNxCBq5"}],"key":"cazChrKY4z"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们不接受无意义的扯皮，只接受有理有据的技术博弈。现在给你们最后选择：要么立即升级至高级技术工程师，要么接受差评并重新开单。」","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"key":"GZJapSxZSt"}],"key":"YXdvMkIRzo"}],"key":"vrHZHICgY3"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"验收标准","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"key":"iIYAFAXtfs"}],"identifier":"id","label":"验收标准","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"yMFcrft8WG"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1},"end":{"line":52,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"成功转型：对方不再要求电话，开始在工单中回复具体技术分析；回复语气从请问/辛苦变为专业的经后台排查/定位发现，说明高级技术工程师已介入；响应速度明显加快，对方表现出怕差评/关单的紧迫感。","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1},"end":{"line":52,"column":1}},"key":"D55IZLzta8"}],"key":"n0m5itX3VH"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":1},"end":{"line":54,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最终验收：故障彻底解决，厂商给出真实根因及预防措施；对方主动或在暗示下提供代金券、服务时长延长或其他额度返还；该厂商将你的账户标记为高专业度/高敏感度客户，未来工单直接进入快速通道。","position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":1},"end":{"line":54,"column":1}},"key":"InIuRvX4GH"}],"key":"pjYvrd9OyL"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":1},"end":{"line":56,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相关资源","position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":1},"end":{"line":56,"column":1}},"key":"CBMkJrWMUN"}],"identifier":"id","label":"相关资源","html_id":"id-4","implicit":true,"key":"VGgC0yW17m"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":58,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":58,"column":1},"end":{"line":58,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"link","url":"/purchase","position":{"start":{"line":58,"column":1},"end":{"line":58,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"采购流程","position":{"start":{"line":58,"column":1},"end":{"line":58,"column":1}},"key":"Zx00iPpEXc"}],"urlSource":"./purchase.md","dataUrl":"/purchase.json","internal":true,"protocol":"file","key":"EL1gW3E6qH"}],"key":"bljfy3ALmf"}],"key":"NAnO3OuR0b"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"link","url":"/index-15","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SCM概览","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"key":"gGpGm8akaj"}],"urlSource":"./index.md","dataUrl":"/index-15.json","internal":true,"protocol":"file","key":"f9bYmG0rzQ"}],"key":"SRwY00q9Jh"}],"key":"UVEAmiSyLN"}],"key":"LzYWMW1sZq"}],"key":"WF1qj5nMT7"}],"key":"QouHJ1f6a2"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}